 *                 directly to Binance USD-M Futures (ExchangeGatewayBinanceFuturesDirectBrokerage).
 *               - Price (OHLCV) from the live 8778 feed as Lean TradeBar.
{%- if subscribe_features %}
 *               - Extra futures/on-chain columns from the 8778 market_features
 *                 stream via MatchXKlineWithCoinglassBar (DQH reflection-fills it).
{%- endif %}
 *
 * The FactorState classes + Rebalance() math below are byte-identical to the
 * backtest composite, so live trades on the SAME composite signal the backtest used.
 *
 * INTEGRATION NOTES (confirm during smoke — see reference/lean_live_composer.md):
 *   1. binance_direct has NO IHistoryProvider wired, so SetWarmUp does NOT backfill.
 *      Ring buffers fill forward from live bars; symbols are skipped (insufficient
 *      bars) until warm. For long-lookback 1d factors this is a multi-day cold start.
 *   2. The market_features subscription symbol must map to the gateway exchange the
 *      same way AddCryptoFuture does; verify features actually arrive in smoke.
 */

